videos.headline: Arizona State strikes first with TD
videos.description: QB Manny Wilkins finds N'Keal Harry in the back of the end zone to give the Sun Devils the lead.

videos.headline: Rosen misses target and gets picked
videos.description: Josh Rosen overthrows his receiver and it is picked off by Arizona State's Chad Adams.

videos.headline: Richard runs it in for Sun Devils TD
videos.description: Demario Richard pounds it in and Arizona State takes advantage of the turnover.

videos.headline: UCLA's Meadors gets pick-six on tip drill
videos.description: Nate Meadors catches the tipped ball and takes it to 27 yards to the house for the pick-six.

videos.headline: Rosen calls his own number for TD
videos.description: Josh Rosen  runs in for the 1-yard touchdown to tie the game.

videos.headline: Wilkins hurdles in for the score
videos.description: Arizona State QB Manny Wilkins leaps over a defender to put the Sun Devils on top.

videos.headline: UCLA's double pass trick play
videos.description: Josh Rosen gets the backward pass and then finds Jordan Lasley for the first down.

videos.headline: Jamabo runs it in for a Bruins TD
videos.description: Soso Jamabo sprints in for the 21-yard score.

videos.headline: UCLA's Olorunfunmi rips off 56-yard run
videos.description: Bolu Olorunfunmi takes a screen pass for 56-yards and in to the red zone.

videos.headline: Olorunfunmi pounds it in for TD
videos.description: Bolu Olorunfunmi runs in to extend UCLA's lead.

videos.headline: Wilkins drops it in to Williams for 47 yards
videos.description: Arizona State's Manny Wilkins hits Kyle Williams on a slant and go for a big gain.

videos.headline: Arizona State blocks punt, scoops and scores TD
videos.description: The Sun Devils block the punt and return it 9 yards for the touchdown to tie the game.

videos.headline: Harry makes tough catch in traffic on 4th down
videos.description: N'Keal Harry comes down with a catch in double coverage on fourth down to keep Arizona State's drive alive.
